 * &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2&gt;The difference is that:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
 *
 * &lt;li&gt;Said annotation wraps entire function, causing more than needed to be ignored
 * (since it does not support being placed before R-value, at time of writing).
 *
